<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038590" n="171r"/>
    <p> Ex <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517026005501">litteris</rs> Tuis<del> sc</del> charissimis <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1719-12-08">8. <del>No</del>Decembris</date> ad me
                              <lb/>datis Te adhucdum bene valere intelligo et maximope<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re gaudeo. Bonam Tibi valetudinem omniaque prospe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ra ex occasione horum festorum Nativitatis Christi
                              <lb/>novique quem brevi auspicabimur anni <add>porro</add> ex animo
                              <lb/>apprecor. De <rs type="person">Nobili</rs> illo scientiarum Mathematicar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>cupido, quem dicis <del>libenter usurum esse inst</del>desiderare
        <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentiam<del> Ag</del> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Adgnati</rs> mei, ipsique non mediocre sala<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rium offerre, locutus sum ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruum</rs>, qui brevi post
        <lb/><rs type="letter">litteras</rs> accepit pro <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">filio</rs> suo scriptas <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1343364833">Fabris</rs>, <add>in</add> quibus
        <lb/>eandem rem <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Adgnato</rs> meo proponit, <subst><del>eumque</del><add>atque</add></subst> omnibus
                              <lb/>modis<del> exhortari</del> persuadere nititur.<del> Ipse Adgnatus</del>
        <lb/><del>meus </del>Si conditiones quas <rs type="person">Vir</rs> iste Nobilis <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Adgnato</rs> meo
                              <lb/>offert<add> tales sint</add>, ut <del>ipsas </del>eas te suadente amplecti possit, <choice><sic>illos</sic><corr>illas</corr></choice> for<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tasse non recusabit; credo autem ipsu<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>et hac de re proxime
                              <lb/><add>ad Te</add> scripturum esse. Si contingat, ut ad Vos eat conditionem
        <lb/>hanc amplexurus, <add>re</add>portabit<del> itaq</del> ipse <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">dissertationem</rs>
        <lb/><subst><del>t</del><add>T</add></subst>uam, cujus lectionem <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> brevi absolvet. Interim
        <lb/>plurimam accipito salutem et <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruo</rs> et <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me, qui
        <lb/>etiam <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117596027">Zendrinum</rs>, <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">nos</hi></abbr> item <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118901125">Smith</rs> et <rs type="person" key="GND">West</rs> pluri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mum <add>meo nomine</add> saluta<del>tis</del>ri cupio.</p> <closer><salute>Vale.</salute> <date><abbr>Dab.</abbr> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> 27. <abbr>Xbris</abbr> 1719.</date></closer>
    <pb facs="1038591" n="171v"/>
    <postscript><p><lb/><abbr>P. S.</abbr> Sum cupidus sciendi nomen illius <rs type="person">Viri Nobilis</rs> et
        <lb/>conditiones, sub quibus <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Adgnatum</rs> meum domi su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> habere
        <lb/>vult.</p></postscript>
</div>
